    content: `<p>Every year the SEO landscape shifts, and 2024 is no exception. For Toronto businesses, staying ahead of these changes is the difference between leading your category and playing catch-up. SA Media tracks these trends across our global markets and translates them into actionable strategy for our clients.</p>
