  {
    slug: `how-to-grow-social-media-presence-toronto`,
    title: `How to Grow Your Social Media Presence in Toronto`,
    date: '2024-10-19',
    category: 'Marketing',
    location: 'Toronto',
    readTime: '6 min',
    excerpt: `A practical guide for Toronto businesses looking to grow their social media presence - what works, what does not, and what SA Media does for clients.`,
    content: `<p>If you are a Toronto business owner or marketing lead asking how to grow your social media presence, this guide is written for you. The advice here is direct and practical - the kind of advice SA Media gives clients on day one of an engagement.</p>
<h2>Step 1: Audit What You Already Have</h2>
